{"data":[{"date":"03:32 19/08","title":"T\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chievo, Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri khen ng\u1ee3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/tit-ngoi-truoc-chievo-ronaldo-van-duoc-hlv-allegri-khen-ngoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Allegri cho r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Serie A d\u00f9 t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Juve v\u00e0 Chievo v\u1eeba qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Real v\u1edbi ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 112 tri\u1ec7u euro. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Ronaldo s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i Italia, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 t\u1ea1i Anh v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng CR7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1ee3t nh\u1ea1t trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u00e0n Serie A. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Allegri v\u1eabn khen ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n theo th\u1eddi gian.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chievo, Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri khen ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chievo, Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri khen ng\u1ee3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/tit-ngoi-truoc-chievo-ronaldo-van-duoc-hlv-allegri-khen-ngoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Allegri khen ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo d\u00f9 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Serie A</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cRonaldo c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t d\u00f9 m\u1edbi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong v\u00f2ng 7 ng\u00e0y qua. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xung quanh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Ronaldo c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Sorrentino \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra v\u00e0i pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1eadn ra. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng di chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u00e0m quen trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch Ronaldo h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus c\u00f3 b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chievo ch\u1ec9 sau 3 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n sau \u0111\u00f3. May m\u1eafn l\u00e0 b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Mattia Bani v\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a Federico Bernardeschi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Juventus:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/chievo-vs-juventus-serie-a-1882018-372-194755.html\">Chievo 2-3 Juventus: Ronaldo im \u1eafng ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Serie A, L\u00e3o b\u00e0 th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/chinh-thuc-juve-chia-tay-marchisio-sau-25-nam-gan-bo-176-194689.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Juve chia tay Marchisio sau 25 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5642","checkdouble":"194772"},{"date":"01:37 19/08","title":"Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Guingamp 1-3 PSG (V\u00f2ng 2 Ligue 1 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/video-tong-hop-guingamp-13-psg-vong-2-ligue-1-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Guingamp. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Kylian Mbappe t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, PSG \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1.</h2><h2>PSG \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Guingamp. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Kylian Mbappe t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, PSG \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1.</h2>\r\nB\u00c0N TH\u1eaeNG<br>\r\nGuingamp: Nolan Roux (20')<br>\r\nPSG: Neymar (pen, 53'), Mbappe (82, 90')<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Guingamp, HLV Thomas Tuchel kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tung v\u00e0o ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Edinson Cavani hay Mbappe. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, PSG \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, PSG c\u00f2n su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf ph\u00fat 13 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Gianluigi Buffon v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn. B\u00f3ng t\u1eeb c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Nolan Roux \u0111\u1eadp ng\u01b0\u1eddi Buffon v\u00e0 t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn x\u00e0 ngang. D\u00f9 Roux \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00eam qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 20, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Colin Dagba c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 Marcus Regis Coco \u0111o\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nguy hi\u1ec3m. Coco chuy\u1ec1n cho Roux d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Guingamp. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t trong hi\u1ec7p 1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, HLV Tuchel bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tung qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c Mbappe v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u. Ph\u00fat 53, Neymar t\u1ef1 \u0111em v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u00e0 anh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho PSG. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a, Guingamp c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00f9i s\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00ec PSG s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t Mbappe thi\u00ean t\u00e0i. V\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ghi 2 b\u00e0n cho PSG \u1edf ph\u00fat 82 v\u00e0 90 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Tuchel l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau 2 tr\u1eadn, PSG v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng \u1edf ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u Ligue 1. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Guingamp \u0111ang t\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 18 sau 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n<br>\r\nGuingamp: Johnsson; Ikoko, Kerbrat, Eboa, Rebocho; Didot (Sorbon 81'), Blas, Coco, Benezet (Rodelin 66'), Thuram (Salibur 75'); Roux<br>\r\nPSG: Buffon; Dagba, Marquinhos, Silva, Meunier; Bernede (Lo Celso 80'), Rabiot, Nkunku (Diaby 74'); Neymar, Di Maria, Weah (Mbappe 46')<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5641","checkdouble":"194767"},{"date":"19:59 18/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 18/8: Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/1/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-188-pogba-duoc-thuong-lon-neu-tu-choi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 18/8.</h2><h2>Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Barca\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 188 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 188 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/mu-se-khong-ban-pogba-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 18/8: Pogba nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Metro \u0111\u01b0a tin ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba s\u1ebd ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3.4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng n\u1ebfu t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Barca. Pogba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi MU s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Pogba ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n l\u00e0 3.4 b\u1ea3ng n\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u1ebft th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Man United v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pogba kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<h2>Negredo s\u1eafp gia nh\u1eadp Monaco</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;T\u1edd RMC Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Negredo \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia nh\u1eadp Monaco t\u1eeb Besiktas. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat m\u1edbi h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin tr\u00ean, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Gonalons ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Sevilla</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd La Gazzetta dello Sport \u0111\u01b0a tin Maxime Gonalons \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Roma cho ph\u00e9p gia nh\u1eadp Sevilla. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.</div>\r\n<h2>Marchisio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn PSG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo ngu\u1ed3n tin tr\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Claudio Marchisio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t Buffon gia nh\u1eadp Paris Saint-Germain sau khi r\u1eddi Juventus. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Marchisio \u0111ang t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t CLB m\u1edbi sau khi chia tay th\u00e0nh Turin. C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng &ldquo;Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed&rdquo; s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn MLS nh\u01b0ng PSG c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi anh v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Monaco theo \u0111u\u1ed5i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n World Cup</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd France Football \u0111\u01b0a tin Monaco \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Domagoj Vida t\u1eeb Besiktas. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Croatia. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Monaco s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra 17 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nGalatasaray nh\u1eafm sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd AMK kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Galatasaray \u0111ang nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Danny Welbeck. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Emirates. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t b\u1ea1o tay \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf Champions League. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 Welbeck kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-178-cuu-sao-psg-khuyen-neymar-toi-real-184-194694.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 17/8: C\u1ef1u sao PSG khuy\u00ean Neymar t\u1edbi Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-sang-ngay-178-barca-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-hau-ve-tiem-nang-184-194638.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 17/8: Barca ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5640","checkdouble":"194759"},{"date":"21:23 18/08","title":"Barca 3-0 Alaves: Messi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Blaugrana ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0 \u00fd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/barca-vs-alaves-la-liga-1882018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i La Liga 2018/19 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Alaves d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1 v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t h\u01a1n 2/3 th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, sau c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm. Th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Coutinho.</h2><h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: BARCA 3-0 ALAVES\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/19/EifXOQ.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>Barca \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a H\u00e8 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf  gi\u1ea3i International Champions Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng khi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t,  h\u1ecd l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y  tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sevilla v\u00e0 Boca Juniors. Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 La Liga v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n  c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 nh\u01b0 \u1edf nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, trong \u0111\u00f3 si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0  ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalunya.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i r\u1ea5t h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ernesto Valverde th\u1eeba t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o  tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n La Liga 2018/19 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Nou Camp, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eadn  n\u00e0o \u1edf La Liga m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc (th\u1eafng 16 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 3 tr\u1eadn). Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u00e0i hoa Andres Iniesta  \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t,  \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0  Arthur Melo, Malcom, Arturo Vidal.</p>\r\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb3ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o trong danh s\u00e1ch xu\u1ea5t  ph\u00e1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n n\u00e0y. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u00e2n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 11 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u0169 t\u1eeb  m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Trong \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1 ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng Sergi Roberto xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf  h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Coutinho, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng  xuy\u00ean \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta hay Rafinha, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c hay  trong giao \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</p>\r\n<p>Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, ch\u1eb3ng r\u00f5 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i do \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng  2-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN m\u00e0 Dembele \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh  Messi vs Suarez. Th\u1ef1c ra, v\u1edbi \u01b0u th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Alves ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n  d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1 (thua 9/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Barca) th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c CLB x\u1ee9 Catalunya s\u1eed  d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra sao kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Barca vs Alaves b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 La Liga 201819 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Barca vs Alaves b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 La Liga 201819 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Truc-tiep-Barca-vs-Alaves-bong-da-La-Liga-201819-hom-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi khi, Lionel Messi l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a Barca v\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\nBarca chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1  Messi v\u1edbi c\u00fa volley n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea9y ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Messi t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng  v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 v\u00e0 Jordi Alba di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng r\u1ed3i tung ra c\u00fa volley c\u0103ng  tr\u00fang v\u00e0o c\u1ea1nh l\u01b0\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1eeda hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u00f4i qua m\u00e0 Barcelona th\u1eadm ch\u00ed r\u1ea5t  hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t, n\u00f3i g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf h\u00e0ng.\r\n<p>\u0110\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 kh\u00e1 ch\u1eb7t, chia th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1edbp che ch\u1eafn c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n v\u00e0  c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i l\u0103n x\u1ea3 song c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5y, Barca t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn,  k\u00e9m s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o m\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u do thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Ivan Rakitic l\u00e0  ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u01b0 ch\u1ea5t nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a. Messi c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u  c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, Blaugrana m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1o ra s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00ean c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n  Alaves. Ph\u00fat 38, Messi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0 x\u00e0 ngang \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e0n  th\u1eafng khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc. Ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e0n em Dembele v\u00e0o th\u1ebf  \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pacheco nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</p>\r\n<p>Ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Barca c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn cho h\u00e0ng  c\u00f4ng khi Coutinho th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Semedo. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Roberto s\u1ebd l\u00f9i xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn vai  tr\u00f2 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f2n Coutinho \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, Barca \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1  kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc, l\u00e0m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Alaves ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1ef1c nh\u1ecdc h\u01a1n.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Coutinho cung dong gop 1 ban cho Barca o tran nay sau khi vao san thay nguoi\" title=\"Coutinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n cho Barca \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/4F32E5DC00000578-6074425-image-a-168_1534629881568.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Coutinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n cho Barca \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<p>Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt khai th\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc cho Barca  kh\u00f4ng ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i Lionel Messi. Ph\u00fat 64, El Pulga l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh  hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n theo ki\u1ec3u c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng t\u1ea7m cao m\u00e0  ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p, s\u00e1t m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra khi h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o  ch\u1eafn nh\u1ea3y l\u00ean b\u1eaft b\u00e0i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alaves b\u1ecb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00ean  kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1eb7n b\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6.000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0i ph\u00fat sau, v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Messi c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba v\u00e0 sau v\u00e0i nh\u1ecbp x\u1eed l\u00fd,  huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00f2ng trong ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 g\u00f3c cao c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n  Alaves nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa d\u1ed9i v\u00e0o khung g\u1ed7 b\u1eadt ra. Ph\u00fat  73, \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t Luis Suarez t\u1ecf th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng vui khi b\u1ecb Pacheco t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i pha d\u1ee9t  \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00e1 hi\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 83 th\u00ec chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou.  Nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Arthur Melo, Coutinho d\u1eabn v\u00e0i nh\u1ecbp lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7  \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ed3i vung ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u00e1i ph\u00e1, h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Pacheco. Nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng 2-0 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft  qu\u1ea3 chung cu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00ec v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Luis Suarez ph\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng  v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 c\u1ee7a Alaves cho Messi kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf ch\u1eafc nh\u01b0 th\u00f3i quen r\u1ed3i tung ra  c\u00fa s\u00fat ch\u00ecm \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, kh\u00f4ng cho Pacheco m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Barca vs Alaves b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 La Liga 201819 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Barca vs Alaves b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 La Liga 201819 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/Truc-tiep-Barca-vs-Alaves-bong-da-La-Liga-201819-hom-nay-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca 3-0 Alaves</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u01b0ng Barca r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ef9 m\u00e3n \u1edf La Liga m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Messi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 then ch\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Barca trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.\u00a0Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi La Liga th\u00ec xem ra, s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0o x\u1ee9ng t\u1ea7m v\u1edbi thi\u00ean t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nBARCELONA (4-3-3): </strong>Marc-Andre ter Stegen; Nelson Semedo (Coutinho 46'), Gerard Pique, Samuel  Umtiti, Jordi Alba; Sergi Roberto, Sergio Busquets (Vidal 85'), Ivan Rakitic; Lionel Messi,  Luis Suarez, Ousmane Dembele (Arthur Melo 78')<br>\r\n<strong>ALAVES (4-1-4-1):</strong> Fernando Pacheco; Martin Aguirregabiria, Victor Laguardia,  Guillermo Maripan, Ruben Duarte; Daniel Torres (Adri\u00e1n Mar\u00edn 68'); Jony (Borja Bast\u00f3n 68'), Mubarak Wakaso, Manu  Garcia, Ibai Gomez; Ruben Sobrino (Burgui 71').<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>C\u00f4ng Minh (TTVN)</strong>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5639","checkdouble":"194762"},{"date":"04:06 19/08","title":"Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/iwobi-keu-goi-cac-dong-doi-dung-day-sau-that-bai-truoc-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea v\u1eeba qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea. \u1ede tr\u1eadn khai m\u00e0n Premier League, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City khi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p qu\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. H\u1ecd b\u1ecb Chelsea d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm 2 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a The Gunners \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi Marcos Alonso t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng cho Chelsea \u1edf ph\u00fat 81 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alex Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alex Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/iwobi-keu-goi-cac-dong-doi-dung-day-sau-that-bai-truoc-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Emery \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ee5t xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 17 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf sau khi v\u00f2ng 2 k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, sao tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 Arsenal v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn. Nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Arsenal x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh, \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn derby London n\u1eefa. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/emery-hai-long-du-arsenal-thua-dang-chelsea-172-194773.html\">Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-chelsea-co-the-tao-ra-ma-thuat-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-194771.html\">Hazard: Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra ma thu\u1eadt d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5638","checkdouble":"194775"},{"date":"04:20 19/08","title":"Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/thua-2-tran-lien-arsenal-cua-emery-te-nhat-sau-26-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery \u0111ang c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Premier League trong v\u00f2ng 26 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Arsenal thay th\u1ebf HLV Wenger t\u1eeb m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua. Sau 22 n\u0103m n\u1eb1m d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Wenger, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Arsenal c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n m\u00ecnh sang m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 HLV Emery. Arsenal kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Man City. Ti\u1ebfp ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ecba Stamford Bridge c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u00e0 Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/thua-2-tran-lien-arsenal-cua-emery-te-nhat-sau-26-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi Arsenal trong v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n. V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Arsenal sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 mu\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n khi Arsenal l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n tay tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng khi b\u1ecb Chelsea d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Iwobi. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Marcos Alonso \u1edf ph\u00fat 81 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n cho The Blues.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n. <strong>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a 1992/93</strong>. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3, Arsenal m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn thua 2-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Norwich tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb Blackburn \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGeorge Graham l\u00e0 HLV d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 1992/93 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 10.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HLV Emery c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Steve Burtenshaw.</strong> Khi n\u1eafm gi\u1eef vai tr\u00f2 HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n, Burtenshaw \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 3 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u00e1ng 3 \u2013 th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m 1986.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5637","checkdouble":"194776"},{"date":"04:30 19/08","title":"Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng, Sarri v\u1eabn d\u00e8 d\u1eb7t khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/khoi-dau-tung-bung-sarri-van-de-dat-khi-noi-ve-cuoc-dua-vo-dich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Sarri cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 coi l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Premier League.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Huddersfield ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thu v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Arsenal tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Stamford Bridge. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Marcos Alonso \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u00fap Chelsea th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 3-2 d\u00f9 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 hai tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV Sarri. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u trong m\u01a1 v\u1edbi The Blues. Nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t, HLV Sarri v\u1eabn e d\u00e8 khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t, HLV Sarri v\u1eabn e d\u00e8 khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/khoi-dau-tung-bung-sarri-van-de-dat-khi-noi-ve-cuoc-dua-vo-dich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng, Sarri v\u1eabn d\u00e8 d\u1eb7t khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cKh\u00f4ng, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong 25 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. Ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p s\u00e1t t\u1ea7m cao kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u00e1p s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u00ec r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i c\u0169ng x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn. V\u1eady n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nEden Hazard m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o thay Willian \u1edf ph\u00fat 60. V\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Alonso ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Hazard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 n\u00ean cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y 25-30 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n cao. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng trong v\u00f2ng 1 tu\u1ea7n ho\u1eb7c c\u00f9ng l\u1eafm l\u00e0 2 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ee7 c\u1ea3 90 ph\u00fat\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem video tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&autoplay=false&mute=false&vtype=1&playType=0&_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&postroll=true&replay=true&nonVol=true&volume=0.6&boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&nopre=true&midroll=0.8;20s&urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5636","checkdouble":"194777"},{"date":"05:26 19/08","title":"3 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/3-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-thang-tung-bung-cua-chelsea-truoc-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong khi Chelsea th\u0103ng hoa v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb v\u00f9i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ef1c th\u1eb3m. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng khoan nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1eefa Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u00eam qua.</h2><h2>H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a hai b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 m\u00e3n nh\u00e3n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V trung l\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Chelsea l\u1eabn Arsenal \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 khi Arsenal li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Bellerin v\u00e0 Monreal. N\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n, Arsenal c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ngay trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Chelsea v\u00e0 Arsenal ch\u01b0a v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Arsenal kh\u00f4ng lui v\u1ec1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn cho h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu 2 b\u00e0n thua, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n thua quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf ph\u00fat 81. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Marcos Alonso b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf tr\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i Arsenal v\u00e0 tung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho Pedro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3, Bellerin b\u1ecb h\u00fat theo Willian v\u00e0 Mkhitaryan th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng lui v\u1ec1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Alonso g\u00e2y nguy hi\u1ec3m. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 Alonso di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba Arsenal m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ai k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArsenal \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n d\u00e2ng qu\u00e1 cao. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 khai th\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng ph\u00eda sau h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m \u0111\u00e1ng kinh ng\u1ea1c trong kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t trong top 4 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu kh\u00e1c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Granit Xhaka n\u00ean ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Xhaka c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean quen thu\u1ed9c h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, Xhaka v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Emery tin t\u01b0\u1edfng trao su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea. Nh\u01b0ng Xhaka kh\u00f4ng s\u1eeda \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 b\u1ecb thay ra ngay sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa hi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xhaka\" title=\"Xhaka\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Xhaka ch\u01b0a thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Emery</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea, Xhaka li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft khi tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Xhaka c\u0169ng t\u1ea1o r\u1ea5t \u00edt \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 Arsenal ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u00e2ng cao. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu trao cho c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng th\u00ec b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ebfn c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ebd t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi Xhaka c\u00f2n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Arsenal kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee7 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 cao h\u01a1n th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7. Nh\u01b0ng khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi s\u00e2n, Arsenal thi tri\u1ec3n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u1ec3 Xhaka ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd HLV Emery c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Torreira v\u00e0 Guendouzi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. N\u1ebfu HLV Emery mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, &ldquo;tr\u1ea3m&rdquo; Xhaka l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea thay \u0111\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n khi c\u00f3 Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111i\u1ec3m sang ph\u00fat 60, HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a ng\u00f4i sao Eden Hazard v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. V\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i mang t\u00ednh b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 30 ph\u00fat nh\u01b0ng Hazard \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Arsenal nhi\u1ec1u phen cho\u00e1ng v\u00e1ng. V\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u b\u1eb1ng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Alonso l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard\" title=\"Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/052423-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Hazard l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o cho Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng Hazard \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 l\u1ea7n ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u1edbi 1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng Hazard s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Newcastle v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 Willian \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng anh thi\u1ebfu \u0111i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Hazard. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 cho nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea. C\u00f3 Hazard tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a The Blues c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 th\u1edf h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00fat g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 l\u00e0m b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Chelsea ra sao ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Hazard.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea 3-2 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279447\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/19/chelsea-arsenal-1534617138.mp4&amp;autoplay=false&amp;mute=false&amp;vtype=1&amp;playType=0&amp;_admParamTvc=0;0;0;0&amp;_listsuggest=https://kenh14s.cnnd.vn/Handler/Video/ListVideoXML.ashx?watch=0&amp;postroll=true&amp;replay=true&amp;nonVol=true&amp;volume=0.6&amp;boxVideoID=ifVideo-0&amp;nopre=true&amp;midroll=0.8;20s&amp;urlParent=http://kenh14.vn/truc-tiep-h2-chelsea-3-2-arsenal-marcos-alonso-lap-cong-20180818161138825.chn\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5635","checkdouble":"194778"},{"date":"05:44 19/08","title":"Arsenal thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp: Unai Emery c\u1ea7n th\u00eam bao nhi\u00eau th\u1eddi gian?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/arsenal-thua-tran-thu-hai-lien-tiep-unai-emery-can-them-bao-nhieu-thoi-gian.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u00eam nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed5 x\u1ebb sau khi Arsenal \u0111\u1ec3 thua Chelsea nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Unai Emery v\u1eabn mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh.</h2><h2>Khi Unai Emery l\u1ea1i xin th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean th\u1ea5y quen thu\u1ed9c nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb Unai Emery sau hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Premier League l\u00e0 c\u00e2u n\u00f3i &quot;ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n&quot;. Unai Emery b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 ra l\u00e0 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi Steve Burtenshaw (1986 - thua ba tr\u1eadn) \u0111\u1ec3 thua trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery da thua trong man dau tri voi Maurizio Sarri.\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 thua trong m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Maurizio Sarri.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/emery-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 thua trong m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Maurizio Sarri.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u theo c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n. C\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e1ch \u1edf h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh do Hector Bellerin \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 n\u01a1i d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua cho Arsenal. Unai Emery y\u00eau c\u1ea7u hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00e2ng cao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i d\u1eabn t\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a Pedro th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi Bellerin \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n ba h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean l\u1ed7 h\u1ed5ng \u0111\u1ec3 Marcos Alonso b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng c\u0103ng ngang cho Pedro l\u00e0m b\u00e0n. B\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 ba c\u0169ng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Bellerin khi Hazard c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o cho Marcos Alonso l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 trong tr\u1eadn thua Man City, c\u1ea3 hai l\u1ea7n th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed Bellerin tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef. Pep Guardiola s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ed3ng c\u00e1nh Sterling - Mendy \u0111\u1ec3 kho\u00e9t th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Bellerin, Maurizio Sarri tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi c\u1eb7p Willian - Marcos Alonso.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vi tri cua Hector Bellerin lien tuc bi khai thac trong hai tran vua qua.\" title=\"V\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Hector Bellerin li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb khai th\u00e1c trong hai tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/bellerin-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>V\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Hector Bellerin li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb khai th\u00e1c trong hai tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o v\u1edbi HLV Unai Emery v\u1ec1 l\u1ed7 h\u1ed5ng trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Arsenal: Bellerin c\u1ea7n th\u00eam s\u1ef1 b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Granit Xhaka tr\u00ean s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u01a1i g\u1ea7n Bellerin h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u00edt c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng xu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng. Vi\u1ec7c HLV Unai Emery ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm thay ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y b\u1eb1ng Lucas Torreira ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o gi\u00fap Bellerin c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 b\u1ecdc l\u00f3t t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Arsenal tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0m b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u. Aubameyang v\u00e0 Mkhitaryan \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng... l\u00ean tr\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 bi quan?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 22 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb \u1edf Arsenal, HLV Arsene Wenger ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua hai tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Unai Emery b\u1ea5t t\u00e0i, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1edfi v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00e1ch quan chi ph\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal\" title=\"Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/thua-2-tran-lien-arsenal-cua-emery-te-nhat-sau-26-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Arsenal thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League 2018-19.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Arsenal g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea. M\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd s\u1eb5n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i lo c\u1ee7a Emery khi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00f4ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p. Sokratis m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, trong khi Granit Xhaka v\u00e0 Mesut Ozil kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn HLV Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, b\u1edfi c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u00f4ng \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1edf Arsenal.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chelsea, HLV Emery t\u1eebng nh\u1eafc kh\u00e9o Mesut Ozil ph\u1ea3i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u01a1n. Vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng r\u00fat c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf ph\u00fat 68 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery co ly do de khong hai long voi mot so cau thu sau khi Arsenal thua tran thu hai lien tiep.\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sau khi Arsenal thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/emery-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Unai Emery c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sau khi Arsenal thua tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, hai tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 gh\u00ea g\u1edbm b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m cu\u1ed1i tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Wenger. Thua hai b\u00e0n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh, Arsenal t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn r\u1ed3i g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a ch\u1ec9 trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh Rome kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y, Unai Emery c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. Ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Man City \u0111\u0103ng quang hay sao?<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chelsea vs Arsenal:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-thang-tung-bung-cua-chelsea-truoc-arsenal-172-194778.html\">3 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khoi-dau-tung-bung-sarri-van-de-dat-khi-noi-ve-cuoc-dua-vo-dich-172-194777.html\">Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng, Sarri v\u1eabn d\u00e8 d\u1eb7t khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thua-2-tran-lien-arsenal-cua-emery-te-nhat-sau-26-nam-172-194776.html\">Thua 2 tr\u1eadn li\u1ec1n, Arsenal c\u1ee7a Emery t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 26 n\u0103m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/iwobi-keu-goi-cac-dong-doi-dung-day-sau-that-bai-truoc-chelsea-172-194775.html\">Iwobi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pochettino-noi-khung-sau-khi-bi-hoi-ve-tuong-lai-alderweireld-172-194774.html\">Pochettino n\u1ed5i kh\u00f9ng sau khi b\u1ecb h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Alderweireld</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/emery-hai-long-du-arsenal-thua-dang-chelsea-172-194773.html\">Emery h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 Arsenal thua \u0111au Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5634","checkdouble":"194779"},{"date":"17:37 18/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Chievo vs Juventus 23h00 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (Serie A 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/18/chievo-vs-juventus-serie-a-1882018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chievo vs Juventus: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Chievo vs Juventus v\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Italia Serie A 2018/19 l\u00fac 23h00 \u0111\u00eam ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 18/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea3m h\u1ecda s\u1eadp c\u1ea7u Morandi \u1edf Genoa khi\u1ebfn 39 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thi\u1ec7t m\u1ea1ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng trong nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y qua. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n Serie A 2018-19 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0 t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Juventus t\u1ea1i Marc'Antonio Bentegodi, s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac 9 n\u0103m ho\u00e0ng kim c\u00f9ng Real Madrid v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u1edbi Juventus. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ec9 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 33. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi Juventus, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 canh b\u1ea1c m\u00e0 coi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chievo vs Juventus b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd Serie A h\u00f4m nay 188 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Chievo vs Juventus b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd Serie A h\u00f4m nay 188 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-chievo-vs-juventus-23h00-ngay-188-serie-a-201819.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chievo vs Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus c\u00f3 l\u00fd do ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u00cdt nh\u1ea5t, Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1edf n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e3n nguy\u1ec7n khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u01a1n s\u1ed1t m\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra \u1edf m\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u1ee7ng. S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ec9 l\u1ee5c b\u00e1n ra l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. N\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n mang l\u1ea1i cho Juventus nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ebfch x\u00f9 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf khi L\u00e3o b\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1t Champions League \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng hay kh\u00f4ng, v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee3i t\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, ho\u1eb7c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 2-3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00eam nay, Cristiano Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft Serie A. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn SV\u0110 Marc'Antonio Bentegodi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 tr\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCris Ronaldo s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c! Anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a NHM v\u00e0 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Serie A d\u00e0nh cho s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. \u0110\u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 CR7 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede Real Madrid, Cris Ronaldo th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u1ec7ch tr\u00e1i. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft Juventus \u0111\u00eam nay, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Allegri \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 CR7 gia t\u0103ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Serie A, chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 9 n\u0103m, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 khai h\u1ecfa, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Deportivo v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2. \u0110\u00eam nay, CR7 k\u00ec v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n th\u1ebf khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Juventus ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 Chievo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5633","checkdouble":"194755"},{"date":"15:30 18/08","title":"B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/bao-thai-chi-ra-guong-mat-duoc-ky-vong-nhat-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Th\u00e1i Lan, SiamSport m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t ASIAD 2018, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0 <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1edd SiamSport \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ec3 t\u00ean 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t ASIAD 2018. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u00f9 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, anh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. D\u00f9 \u1edf\u00a0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng nh\u1edd t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i ch\u1ec9 ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/cong-phuong_vwzy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ecdt\u00a0danh s\u00e1ch 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, t\u1edd SiamSport b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng xem nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i sau lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan v\u1eeba qua, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd khi s\u00fat h\u1ecfng \u0111\u1ebfn 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n tuy nhi\u00ean, anh v\u1eabn c\u00f3 cho ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n cho Quang H\u1ea3i m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Sau hai l\u1ea7n s\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1ee3t penalty, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eeb pha che ch\u1eafn th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1eddi Olympic Pakistan. V\u00ec l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, SiamSport c\u00f2n nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi Son Heung-min, Lee Seung-woo (H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c), Beto Goncalves (Indonesia), Mohammed Darwish (Palestine), Adel Bader (Qatar), Zhang Yuning (Trung Qu\u1ed1c), Aung Thu (Myanmar) v\u00e0 Supachai (Th\u00e1i Lan). \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5632","checkdouble":"194745"},{"date":"15:42 18/08","title":"HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung: \u201c\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/hlv-mai-duc-chung-dt-viet-nam-se-danh-bai-thai-lan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 18 di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 18h30 ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi, HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/HLV-Mai-Duc-Chung-DT-Viet-Nam-se-danh-bai-Thai-Lan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u1edf ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e1 th\u0103m may r\u1ee7i \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef ASIAD 2018. Theo \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm 2 t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu h\u1ea1 Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19 t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2: \u201cX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m v\u00f3c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan lu\u00f4n k\u1ecb gi\u01a1 nhau v\u1edbi nhau. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng SEA Games v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang ta. \u1ede AFF Cup 2018, Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i Th\u00e1i Lan. Qua theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung cao nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 99%. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.\u00a0<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-mai-duc-chung-chi-ra-2-dieu-kien-de-dt-viet-nam-du-world-cup-465-188358.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/hlv-mai-duc-chung-chi-ra-2-dieu-kien-de-dt-viet-nam-du-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-mai-duc-chung-chi-ra-2-dieu-kien-de-dt-viet-nam-du-world-cup-465-188358.html\">HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung ch\u1ec9 ra 2 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 World Cup</span><br>\r\nHLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n d\u1ef1 World Cup, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n hai v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-myanmar-16h00-ngay-hom-nay-137-372-191100.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/video-tong-hop-nu-viet-nam-30-nu-myanmar-aff-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-myanmar-16h00-ngay-hom-nay-137-372-191100.html\">N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 N\u1eef Myanmar (KT): Th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm, n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111o\u1ea1t h\u1ea1ng 3 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1</span><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng th\u1eafng 4-3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng 3 chung cu\u1ed9c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef \u0110\u00f4ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-australia-16h00-ngay-117-372-190944.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-australia-16h00-ngay-117.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-australia-16h00-ngay-117-372-190944.html\">N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-4 U20 N\u1eef Australia (KT): Thua b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e0nh tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 khu v\u1ef1c</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 thua to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Australia \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018. Tuy\u1ebft Dung l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi c\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n cho...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5631","checkdouble":"194746"},{"date":"16:21 18/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nguoi-nhat-se-dung-thu-mon-du-bi-de-dau-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh Kojima Ryosuke d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan n\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Pakistan c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt l\u00e0 Kojima Ryosuke \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 90 ph\u00fat sau va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn cho Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t n\u1eb7ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/a6-3120-1534566074.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Obi Obinna l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan, ch\u00ednh HLV Moriyasu Hajime c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u00f4ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i VCK U20 World Cup c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cKojima Ryosuke d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u201d, HLV Moriyasu Hajime cho bi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Obi Obinna cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Obi Obinna l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 b\u1ed1 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 77 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft thay cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Ryosuke. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 b\u1eaft ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i\u201d, Obi n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 \u1edf 1 trong 3 b\u1ea3ng B/E/F \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out.\u00a0<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-olympic-viet-nam-chat-luong-hon-sau-giai-u23-chau-a-2018-472-194738.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-olympic-viet-nam-chat-luong-hon-sau-giai-u23-chau-a-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/hlv-olympic-nhat-ban-olympic-viet-nam-chat-luong-hon-sau-giai-u23-chau-a-2018-472-194738.html\">HLV Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n sau gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018</span><br />\r\n\u00d4ng Hajime Moriyasu \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang-seo \u1edf ASIAD 18 v\u00ec l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5630","checkdouble":"194747"}]}